[
  {
    "text": "A symbiote.",
    "start": 0.023,
    "end": 0.72,
    "scene_id": 1
  },
  {
    "text": "Alien.",
    "start": 1.161,
    "end": 1.579,
    "scene_id": 1
  },
  {
    "text": "Alive.",
    "start": 2.043,
    "end": 2.531,
    "scene_id": 1
  },
  {
    "text": "And desperate for a host. (page 3",
    "start": 3.042,
    "end": 4.969,
    "scene_id": 1
  },
  {
    "text": "panel 0)",
    "start": 4.969,
    "end": 5.573,
    "scene_id": 1
  },
  {
    "text": "Ben Grimm arrives at the Baxter Building",
    "start": 5.573,
    "end": 7.268,
    "scene_id": 2
  },
  {
    "text": "searching for Reed — but finds something",
    "start": 7.268,
    "end": 9.102,
    "scene_id": 2
  },
  {
    "text": "far more dangerous waiting beneath a sheet.",
    "start": 9.102,
    "end": 10.867,
    "scene_id": 2
  },
  {
    "text": "(page 4 panel 2)",
    "start": 11.494,
    "end": 12.376,
    "scene_id": 2
  },
  {
    "text": "Reed explains the symbiote enhances its host's",
    "start": 12.376,
    "end": 14.396,
    "scene_id": 3
  },
  {
    "text": "emotions, latching onto their conscience.",
    "start": 14.396,
    "end": 16.486,
    "scene_id": 3
  },
  {
    "text": "Ben listens... too closely. (page 9 panel",
    "start": 16.881,
    "end": 20.271,
    "scene_id": 3
  },
  {
    "text": "0)",
    "start": 20.271,
    "end": 20.759,
    "scene_id": 3
  },
  {
    "text": "The symbiote speaks directly to Ben's deepest",
    "start": 20.921,
    "end": 22.872,
    "scene_id": 4
  },
  {
    "text": "desire: to look human again.",
    "start": 22.872,
    "end": 24.845,
    "scene_id": 4
  },
  {
    "text": "It offers him everything Reed cannot. (page",
    "start": 25.426,
    "end": 28.05,
    "scene_id": 4
  },
  {
    "text": "9 panel 1)",
    "start": 28.05,
    "end": 28.746,
    "scene_id": 4
  },
  {
    "text": "Ben's body begins to change.",
    "start": 28.746,
    "end": 30.232,
    "scene_id": 5
  },
  {
    "text": "Black tendrils consume him.",
    "start": 30.79,
    "end": 32.067,
    "scene_id": 5
  },
  {
    "text": "The Thing — becoming something else entirely.",
    "start": 32.717,
    "end": 35.619,
    "scene_id": 5
  },
  {
    "text": "(page 14 panel 4)",
    "start": 35.991,
    "end": 37.082,
    "scene_id": 5
  },
  {
    "text": "Reed realizes the terrible truth: removing the",
    "start": 37.082,
    "end": 39.474,
    "scene_id": 6
  },
  {
    "text": "symbiote means Ben loses his humanity forever.",
    "start": 39.474,
    "end": 42.005,
    "scene_id": 6
  },
  {
    "text": "He calls it his responsibility to be",
    "start": 42.4,
    "end": 43.909,
    "scene_id": 6
  },
  {
    "text": "a monster. (page 13 panel 3)",
    "start": 43.909,
    "end": 46.184,
    "scene_id": 6
  },
  {
    "text": "In the chaos, Venom — Ben's symbiote",
    "start": 46.184,
    "end": 48.274,
    "scene_id": 7
  },
  {
    "text": "form — kills Reed Richards.",
    "start": 48.274,
    "end": 49.83,
    "scene_id": 7
  },
  {
    "text": "Snaps his neck right in front of",
    "start": 50.039,
    "end": 51.13,
    "scene_id": 7
  },
  {
    "text": "him. (page 28 panel 1)",
    "start": 51.13,
    "end": 52.779,
    "scene_id": 7
  },
  {
    "text": "Ben weeps over Reed's body, blaming himself.",
    "start": 52.779,
    "end": 54.66,
    "scene_id": 8
  },
  {
    "text": "The symbiote whispers: there is no Fantastic",
    "start": 55.031,
    "end": 57.144,
    "scene_id": 8
  },
  {
    "text": "Four.",
    "start": 57.144,
    "end": 57.562,
    "scene_id": 8
  },
  {
    "text": "There is only us. (page 29 panel",
    "start": 57.771,
    "end": 59.791,
    "scene_id": 8
  },
  {
    "text": "2)",
    "start": 59.791,
    "end": 60.233,
    "scene_id": 8
  },
  {
    "text": "But Ben rejects the symbiote's words.",
    "start": 60.534,
    "end": 62.346,
    "scene_id": 9
  },
  {
    "text": "With pure rage, he roars: It's just",
    "start": 62.624,
    "end": 65.295,
    "scene_id": 9
  },
  {
    "text": "me. (page 29 panel 4)",
    "start": 65.295,
    "end": 67.5,
    "scene_id": 9
  },
  {
    "text": "We make monsters.",
    "start": 67.5,
    "end": 68.36,
    "scene_id": 10
  },
  {
    "text": "We feed them our grief, our anger,",
    "start": 68.87,
    "end": 70.682,
    "scene_id": 10
  },
  {
    "text": "our insecurity.",
    "start": 70.682,
    "end": 71.587,
    "scene_id": 10
  },
  {
    "text": "And they hold up a mirror. (page",
    "start": 72.284,
    "end": 74.385,
    "scene_id": 10
  },
  {
    "text": "30 panel 3)",
    "start": 74.385,
    "end": 75.442,
    "scene_id": 10
  }
]